{
  "page": "East Gate",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Winterfell_map.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ac/Winterfell_map.png/350px-Winterfell_map.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"384\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/a/ac/Winterfell_map.png 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Winterfell_map.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Fan-made map of Winterfell before <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>. 1.North Gate 2.<a href=\"/index.php/Broken_Tower\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Broken Tower\">Broken Tower</a> 3.<a href=\"/index.php/Glass_Gardens\" title=\"Glass Gardens\">Glass Gardens</a> 4.<a href=\"/index.php/Crypt_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Crypt of Winterfell\">Crypts</a> 5.<a href=\"/index.php/First_Keep\" title=\"First Keep\">First Keep</a> 6.<a href=\"/index.php/Godswood_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Godswood of Winterfell\">Godswood</a> 7.<a href=\"/index.php/Guards_Hall\" title=\"Guards Hall\">Guards Hall</a> 8.<a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">East Gate</a> 9.Armory 10.<a href=\"/index.php/Hunter%27s_Gate\" title=\"Hunter&#39;s Gate\">Hunter's Gate</a> 11.Kennels 12.<a href=\"/index.php/Guest_House\" title=\"Guest House\">Guest House</a> 13. Bridge between the armory and the Great Keep 14.<a href=\"/index.php/Great_Keep_(Winterfell)\" title=\"Great Keep (Winterfell)\">Great Keep</a> 15.Maester's turret 16.Kitchen 17.Courtyard 18.<a href=\"/index.php/Bell_Tower\" title=\"Bell Tower\">Bell Tower</a> 19.<a href=\"/index.php/Library_Tower\" title=\"Library Tower\">Library Tower</a> 20.<a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Catelyn%27s_sept\" title=\"Lady Catelyn&#39;s sept\">Sept</a> 21.Stables 22.<a href=\"/index.php/Great_Hall_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Great Hall of Winterfell\">Great Hall</a> 23.Smithy 24.South Gate</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>East Gate</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> or <b>east gate</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> is one of the gates of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>. Situated along the east of the castle, it leads to the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsroad\" title=\"Kingsroad\">kingsroad</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The <b>Kingsroad Gate</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> may thus be another name for the same gate.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=East_Gate&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=East_Gate&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>In the aftermath of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Sack of Winterfell\">sack of Winterfell</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Osha\" title=\"Osha\">Osha</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Rickon_Stark\" title=\"Rickon Stark\">Rickon Stark</a> take the East Gate to the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsroad\" title=\"Kingsroad\">kingsroad</a> when they depart the castle.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=East_Gate&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Since the Kingsroad Gate has not been used recently, ice freezes its drawbridge chains.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> When Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_North\" title=\"Warden of the North\">Warden of the North</a>, decides to send the feuding <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">Freys</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Manderly\" title=\"House Manderly\">Manderlys</a> against <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>, he orders the Freys to gather by Winterfell's main gates and the Manderlys by the east gate.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=East_Gate&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Believe I'll try the East Gate, and follow the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsroad\" title=\"Kingsroad\">kingsroad</a> a ways.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Osha\" title=\"Osha\">Osha</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen Reed</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=East_Gate&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_69\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 69\">Chapter 69</a>, Bran VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_51\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 51\">Chapter 51</a>, Theon I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_46\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 46\">Chapter 46</a>, A Ghost in Winterfell.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405033309\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.029 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.031 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 820/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8876/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3033/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 327/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2825/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   18.145      1 -total\n 78.81%   14.301      8 Template:Ref\n 51.10%    9.272      8 Template:Ref/core\n 13.62%    2.472      1 Template:References\n 12.10%    2.195      1 Template:Quote\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:39820-0!canonical and timestamp 20260405033308 and revision id 332317\n -->\n",
